üè° Lead & Tour Flow

User action ‚Üí Fills ScheduleTourForm or LeadForm on frontend.

Next.js service ‚Üí Calls leadService.ts / alertService.ts ‚Üí hits /automation/leads/lead-capture.json.

n8n workflow ‚Üí Validates + enriches ‚Üí pushes to CRM (HubSpot/Airtable).

Optional ‚Üí Syncs to calendar (Google/Outlook) for tour booking.

Comms ‚Üí Sends confirmation via SendGrid/WhatsApp to user + notification to Realtor.
